    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Why marts'>
      <style />
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='32281' id='26' is-fixed='true' type-v2='layout-basic' w='35467' x='63950' y='951'>
            <zone h='32281' id='27' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='35467' x='63950' y='951'>
              <zone fixed-size='106' h='32281' id='49' is-fixed='true' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='7726' x='63950' y='951' />
              <zone h='32281' id='88' type-v2='dashboard-object' w='22522' x='71676' y='951'>
                <button action='tabdoc:goto-sheet window-id=&quot;{A36318C8-FE36-4652-912A-C5E28F64B814}&quot;'>
                  <button-visual-state>
                    <image-path>//wsl.localhost/Ubuntu/home/vivian/_Project_M2_DataEngeering/BlueRose.png</image-path>
                    <tooltip-text>5 Core Marts Portfolio</tooltip-text>
                  </button-visual-state>
                </button>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='65634' id='28' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='63367' x='583' y='951'>
            <zone fixed-size='94' forceUpdate='true' h='12128' id='12' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='63367' x='583' y='951'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontsize='20'>Why Rose Data Marts Matter?</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='470' forceUpdate='true' h='53506' id='15' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='63367' x='583' y='13079'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='15'>From Trusted ‘Golden’ Data Lakehouse to Actionable, Business-Ready Insights — Powered by Blue Rose Marts</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>1. The Challenge (Before)</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>     •  Data Silos</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Raw data is fragmented across sources and lacks consistency </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>     •  High Latency</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Complex queries on raw data are slow and resource-intensive </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>     •  Metric Drift</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Different teams report conflicting definitions of key metrics (e.g., “Revenue”) </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>2. The Strategic Value of Blue Rose Marts</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Performance</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Pre-aggregated, optimized tables significantly improve dashboard speed (up to 80% faster) </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Governance</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Role-based access control ensures secure and controlled data usage </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Consistency</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Standardized KPI definitions create a single source of truth across the organization </run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='33353' id='8' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='35467' x='63950' y='33232'>
            <zone forceUpdate='true' h='33353' id='18' type-v2='text' w='35467' x='63950' y='33232'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>3. Key Outcomes — Blue Rose Marts</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Cost Efficiency</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Reduced compute costs by querying smaller, well-modeled datasets instead of raw data </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Self-Service BI</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Enables analysts to build reports independently without complex SQL joins </run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>    •  Reliability</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>: Ensures high data quality through automated testing in the transformation layer (e.g., dbt tests)</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone h='32464' id='29' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98834' x='583' y='66585'>
            <zone fixed-size='319' h='32464' id='32' is-fixed='true' is-scaled='1' param='//wsl.localhost/Ubuntu/home/vivian/_Project_M2_DataEngeering/Gold_dwh.png' type-v2='bitmap' w='23834' x='583' y='66585'>
